title: 5 minutes with NHRA driver Erica Enders: 'We just decided to rise above it and let the scoreboard do our talking' (video)
text:
Erica Enders covered a lot of topics at the end of her victory Sunday at the NHRA AAA Texas Fall Nationals at Texas Motorplex in Ennis.
Enders spent more than five minutes on her history at Texas Motorplex, tension and rivalries in the pit area, the Disney movie based on her childhood, her road to becoming a Pro Stock driver and going from underdog status to points leader.
